OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSchools failing children   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwith allergies - report    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The mother of a boy who died after     
OL,6, having an allergic reaction at school  
OL,7, has called for changes to the law.     
OL,9,FFive-year-old Benedict Blythe collapsed
OL,10,Fat a school near Peterborough in 2021  
OL,11,Fand the cause of his anaphylaxis is    
OL,12,Funknown.                               
OL,14,FHis mother set up the Benedict Blythe  
OL,15,FFoundation, which has found failings in
OL,16,Fhow schools manage allergies.          
OL,18,FThe Department for Education said      
OL,19,Fchildren with allergies should be      
OL,20,Fsupported at school.                   
